title: Casio Women's LA670WGA-1DF Daily Alarm Digital Gold-tone Watch
feature: Gold-tone watch featuring cushion-shape black dial with digital display
Features alarm, timer, and perpetual calendar functions;Stopwatch
25 mm stainless steel case with mineral dial window and quartz movement
Stainless steel band with fold-over clasp
description: Casio Womens Daily Alarm Gold Tone Digital Watch The quartz-powered Casio Women's LA670WGA-1DF Daily Alarm Digital Gold-tone Watch brings a retro edge to your look. It features a digital-gold dial face with a black background, encased in a sturdy mineral dial window. An easy-to-read time-display format and handy perpetual calendar function ensures your time-telling convenience. Both the gold-tone stationary bezel and 25-millimeter case are made of high-quality stainless steel, and the matching gold-tone band is accompanied by a steadfast fold-over-clasp closure. This affordable, precise timepiece is versatile enough for everyday wear.
